cs.CR, cs.IR, cs.DB, cs.CY, cs.LG

The paper discusses the challenges of commercializing IoT generated personal data and proposes a decentralized marketplace model to address these challenges. This suggests that the paper could belong to the categories of computer security (cs.CR), information retrieval (cs.IR), and databases (cs.DB) as these are relevant to the privacy and security concerns of personal data. Additionally, the paper discusses the licensing framework for data use and access, which could fall under the category of cybernetics (cs.CY). Finally, the paper proposes a model that assesses and modifies transaction risks, which could be related to machine learning (cs.LG) as it involves modeling and prediction.
